==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Gemmary
<hw>Gem"ma*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A receptacle for
jewels or gems; a jewel house; jewels or gems, collectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gemmate</ent>⟦br⟧
